<img src="https://img.freepik.com/free-photo/doctor-with-stethoscope-hands-hospital-background_1423-1.jpg">

</div>

<div class="about-text">

<h2>About DocApp</h2>

<p>
DocApp is a modern online doctor appointment booking system designed
to simplify healthcare access for everyone. Our platform connects patients
with trusted and verified doctors from various specialties.
We provide fast and secure appointment booking with real-time availability.
Patients can easily find doctors based on their needs and book instantly.
Our system helps reduce waiting time and improves healthcare efficiency.
DocApp ensures complete privacy and security of patient data.
The platform is mobile-friendly and easy to use for all age groups.
We aim to make healthcare accessible anytime and anywhere.
Thousands of users trust our system for their medical needs.
DocApp is built using modern technology for reliability and speed.
</p>

